BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Insurance and the Louisiana
Department of Health, in conducting the study, may consult with stakeholders and interested
parties, including healthcare providers, patient advocacy organizations, laboratories,
insurers, and managed care organizations.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that one print copy and one electronic copy of the
report produced pursuant to this Resolution shall be submitted to the David R. Poynter
Legislative Research Library as required by R.S. 24:772.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
commissioner of insurance and the secretary of the Louisiana Department of Health.
